Congratulatory message to Kim Jong Il from NDFSK central committee
 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Pyongyang, February 16 (KCNA) -- General Secretary Kim Jong Il received a congratulatory message from the central committee of the National Democratic Front of South Korea on Feb. 16, his 57th birthday.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
   The message says:
   You, the respected marshal endowed with literary and military accomplishments, loyalty and filial piety, embarked upon the road of revolution in your early years and have led the socialist cause of Juche and the human cause of independence to the road of a certain victory with your brilliant intelligence and extraordinary leadership, performing great, immortal exploits in the annals of revolution.
   You systematized the Juche idea in an integral way, comprehensively developed it in depth and perfected the theory on socialism as a scientific doctrine with your extraordinary intelligence so that Juche Korea could advance vigorously along the track of Juche without the slightest turns and twists  and the people struggling for independence and socialism could advance under the ever-victorious banner.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
   The most beautiful flower garden of loyalty and filial piety and moral obligation has spread, the whole army and all the people are becoming rifles and bombs defending their lader with their lives, an artificial satellite "Kwangmyongsong 1" was launched into orbit to record the stamina of a matchless country in the history of space and their rifles have been loaded with bullets of merciless vengeance sending shivers down the spine of the enemies with such annihilating grit and courage that the earth will cease to exist without Juche Korea. This world startling miracle shines as grand edifice of the era.
   It is the greatest fortune and highest honor for the Korean nation and progressive humankind to hold you in high esteem as an outstanding leader in the era of independence.
   The people in the south are now waging a sacred struggle, invariably and ardently revering you.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 
   The NDFSK will wage a more powerful struggle against the United States and its stooges and for reunification, collaborating with communism and the north under the uplifted banner of the struggle against outside forces and for independence, as required by  the prevailing situation and the development of the revolutionary movement, and thus certainly bring about a new signal turning-point in the national democratic movement.
   The NDFSK central committee wholeheartedly wished Marshal Kim Jong Il a long life in good health, representing the unanimous wish of all the vanguard fighters and patriotic people of all walks of life in the south, says the message.

Congratulatory message to Kim Jong Il from Chongryon central standing committee
 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Pyongyang, February 16 (KCNA) -- General Secretary Kim Jong Il received a congratulatory message from the central standing committee of the General Association of Korean Residents in Japan (Chongryon), on Feb. 16, his 57th birthday.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
   The message says:
   You, the respected Marshal Kim Jong Il, are a great statesman, an iron-willed commander and a benevolent father of the people who has performed undying feats for the country, the nation, the era and humankind by leading to victory and glory for decades the struggle to carry forward and accomplish the revolutionary cause of Juche, started by the fatherly leader Generalissimo Kim Il Sung, with your extraordinary ideological and theoretical intelligence and outstanding leadership ability. 
   You broke a new ground in the cause of making the leader immortal, unprecedented in history, with your purest loyalty and filial piety and moral obligation and made sure that the revolutionary life and immortal feats of the Generalissimo shine long down through generations.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
   The wise leadership of you who unfolded a bright blueprint for building a powerful socialist nation and made a breakthrough in bringing about a great turn through your ceaseless on-site guidance to put it into practice is implanting conviction of victory and optimism about the rise of powerful and prosperous Kim Il Sung's Korea in near future in the mind of all the fellow countrymen.
   Chongryon officials and Koreans in Japan could firmly defend their organisation and build up the tower of patriotism and allegiance higher true to the ever-victorious teachings given by you, cherishing the immovable faith that only when they are led by you can they win in face of the anti-DPRK, anti-Chongryon moves unprecedented since the formation of Chongryon.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
   We will make a tangible contribution to building a powerful nation in the same spirit as that of the people in the homeland who are out in the second Chollima grand march in order to bring about a great turn in the building of a powerful nation.
   The central standing committee of Chongryon wholeheartedly wished Marshal Kim Jong Il a long life in good health, representing the reverence of all the Chongryon officials and Koreans in Japan for him, says the message.
